snippet.title: Glamour Magazine UK
snippet.description:
GLAMOUR is your guide to the latest beauty trends and expert knowledge, fashion and entertainment news, inspirational videos and life advice. 

Mad about beauty? Don’t forget to join the GLAMOUR Beauty Club to test out all the newest products and join in the conversation.
